Package com.insebre.project.model

Class SuperCollection<T>

java.lang.Object
com.insebre.project.model.SuperCollection<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of elements stored in the collection.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, SequencedCollection<T>, Set<T>
public class SuperCollection<T> extends Object implements List<T>, Set<T>, Serializable
A flexible collection implementation that can behave like ArrayList or TreeSet based on its type.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Ismael Semmar Galvez
